}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Ornela Flores";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2992:"<h4>We are pleased to announce the recent integration of <a href="https://wpml.org/">WPML</a> and <a href="http://translations.mcfelder.com/">McFelder Translations</a>, a multiservice technical translation agency.<a href="https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wpmlMcFelder.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1444958" src="https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wpmlMcFelder-300x176.png" alt="" width="300" height="176" srcset="https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wpmlMcFelder-300x176.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wpmlMcFelder-150x88.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wpmlMcFelder.png 371w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></h4>\n<p>McFelder Translations is a translation company focused on the health, technology, marketing, and corporate real estate sectors.</p>\n<p>With more than 6,000 translators and interpreters worldwide, its pool of professional translators enables McFelder to translate a variety of subjects in over 90 languages across thousands of language pairs.</p>\n<p>Its target audience includes international businesses and companies with multimillion-dollar revenues that need integrated technology, processes, and languages to ensure projects run smoothly—from simple to complex projects that require highly specialized and in-depth technical terminology used in welding and cutting, dental implants, and biotechnology.</p>\n<blockquote><p><em>“McFelder Translations understands that a company´s website is most probably one of its most valuable assets. For this reason, a multilingual website is fundamental for international businesses. Any translation company that offers fast and efficient translation of a WordPress website via the WPML Integration is ahead of the field.”</em></p>\n<p><em>Dr. Fiona McCrae, McFelder Director </em></p></blockquote>\n<p>If you are already a WPML user and interested in using McFelder for translation, follow the instructions for<a href="https://wpml.org/translation-service/mcfelder-translations/"> translating WordPress sites with McFelder</a>. If you are new to WPML, feel free to purchase the <a href="https://wpml.org/purchase/">Multilingual CMS</a> package and get started.</p>\n<p><em> </em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=vI7mPmgYBBI:HvHgjc5ycQU:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=vI7mPmgYBBI:HvHgjc5ycQU:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=vI7mPmgYBBI:HvHgjc5ycQU:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=vI7mPmgYBBI:HvHgjc5ycQU:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=vI7mPmgYBBI:HvHgjc5ycQU:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=vI7mPmgYBBI:HvHgjc5ycQU:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/vI7mPmgYBBI" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:89:"https://wpml.org/2017/11/wpml-and-mcfelder-translations-join-into-a-new-partnership/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:84:"https://wpml.org/2017/11/wp