";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15:"Mohamed Khafaja";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4242:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-995848" src="https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header-300x90.png" alt="Compatible Plugins-Header" width="400" height="121" srcset="https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header-300x90.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header-150x45.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header.png 680w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible plugins.</p>\n<p>The plugins are: <a href="https://wp-livechat.com/" rel="noopener" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">WP Live Chat Support</a>, <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/groups/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Groups</a>, <a href="https://codecanyon.net/item/wordpress-live-chat-plugin/3952877" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Screets Live Chat</a>, <a href="https://multiratingpro.com/" rel="noopener" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Multi Rating Pro</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">WP Live Chat Support</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WP Live Chat Support is a fully functioning live chat solution which allows you to engage with clients on your site, increase sales, and offer hands on support.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wp-livechat.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase WP Live Chat Support</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Groups</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Groups is a membership and content access control plugin</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/groups/" target="_blank">Download Groups</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Screets Live Chat</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Chat with your customers on your site for sales and support easily</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://codecanyon.net/item/wordpress-live-chat-plugin/3952877" target="_blank">Purchase Screets Live Chat</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Multi Rating Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Multi Rating allows visitors to rate a post based on multiple criteria and questions.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://multiratingpro.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Multi Rating Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a hr