ml.org/?p=1425638";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:338:"Today we are happy to announce several WPML compatible themes. The themes are: Inka, Amy Gallerix, Smart, Royal, Ambra If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here: Multilingual Ready Themes Multilingual Ready Plugins Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15:"Mohamed Khafaja";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4863:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-975307" src="https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png" alt="WPML Compatible themes" width="400" height="112" srcset="https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-150x42.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1.png 568w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce several WPML compatible themes.</p>\n<p>The themes are: <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/inka-minimal-blog-wordpress-theme/20583761" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Inka</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/gallerix-creative-gallery-portfolio-and-blog-theme/20725461" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Amy Gallerix</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/smart-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/17333318" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Smart</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/royal-responsive-one-page-parallax-wordpress-theme/19560027" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Royal</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/ambra-minimal-marketplace-wordpress-theme/20169380" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Ambra</a> </p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Inka</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Inka is a minimal blogging WordPress theme for traveling, fashion food and lifestyles blogs.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/inka-minimal-blog-wordpress-theme/20583761" target="_blank">Purchase Inka</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Amy Gallerix</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Amy Gallerix theme is a clean and professional WordPress theme for photography, creative portfolio, and blog site.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/gallerix-creative-gallery-portfolio-and-blog-theme/20725461" target="_blank">Purchase Amy Gallerix</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Smart</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Smart is a multi-purpose theme suitable for any type of publisher.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/smart-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/17333318" target="_blank">Purchase Smart</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Royal</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Royal is a clean and modern one page WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/royal-responsive-one-page-parallax-wordpress-theme/19560027" target="_blank">Purchase Royal</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Ambra</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Minimal Marketplace WordPress Theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/ambra-minimal-marketplace-wordpress-theme/20169380" target="_blank">Purchase Ambra</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=pPvd2PNeFWI:Nf41ju-E6ng:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/pPvd2PNeFWI" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"comm